Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要招待各位貴賓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好吃的料理 飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有表演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌 跳舞和變魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 燈里妳會這麼多東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我以為藍華妳會的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危機了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 在AQUA的日曆上 今天開始就是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們領航員也換上了冬裝制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亞利亞社長…你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早到晚都非常舒適宜人的這幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為秋天的觀光季節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那個節日的到來 城中的人會開始變多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟要通過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那邊如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:06.09,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 邂逅的結晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了啊 比平時更呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 前輩今天好像沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…小愛一直都沒回我電郵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 她好像跟妳說她奶奶身體不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不是說要來參加Redentore的慶典嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}Redentore：每年7月的第三個星期六舉行的慶典 Redentore\N意為「救世主耶穌基督」 慶典當日會從Zattere築起船橋通往\NGiudecca的Redentore教會供人們前往參拜 晚上則舉行煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說是想看我的新鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是她學業太忙碌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大概就會回我電郵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一周就到Redentore了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩們今年打算怎麼過Redentore呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋每年都會開公司派對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我可能會跟晃前輩在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去年接到艾莉西亞前輩的熟客的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年小愛要是能來的話 我打算跟她一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 話說小後輩去年是怎麼過的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明過節的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Redentore不是徹夜狂歡的節日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第二天還要去上學的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今年的話第二天是休息日 所以沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃前輩跟雅典娜前輩也在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有種不好的預感…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…三大精靈為何會聚在一起呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 又是特訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓嗎 嗯 也可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 燈里 我要提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Redentore是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…Redentore就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的威尼斯城的貴族之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先展開的夏日慶典…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐在各種各樣的船上 一起玩樂到天亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後慢慢地演變成了新威尼斯初秋的風景詩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點結巴 不過勉強算合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…莫非今年是我們六個人一起過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里妳們三個負責招待客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責招待客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了準備飯菜和飲料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要負責內部裝飾和活動的時間表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很值得一試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次能招待很多客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是大顯身手的好機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳統料理的調味 還有配合飯菜口味的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊 我們特別為妳們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了Redentore專用的大船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修行啊 修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們都要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是傷腦筋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我們三個人真的能安排好一艘大船嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好早啊 小後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後直接過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為想儘快給兩位前輩看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天午休的時候我試著做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們大船的邀請函？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 愛麗絲 這個很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非妳其實很期待Redentore的修行嗎 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 既然如此 就要好好地幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會加油的 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會超級加油的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把飯菜和飲料放到最後去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先決定要邀請誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大船的搭載人數 加上我們一共能乘12人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還能請9個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 晃前輩和雅典娜前輩不能漏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員大叔 曉先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 燈里 妳要好好想想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳好像很多朋友的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那藍華想請誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們明天就把邀請函發出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能再請一個 找誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想請小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級贊成的說 但是來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 離Redentore只有一周了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她說絕對要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想等她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 那我再給她發一個邀請函的電郵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到Redentore的話 就是鴨肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於怎麼醃製啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 太硬的話老年人會咬不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魚和蔬菜來平衡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母喜不喜歡蘑菇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們都試著做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在試做料理期間 雖然充滿了不安和失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 燈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們所做的一切 都是前所未有地新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓時間飛快地溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我們邀請的客人 能夠享受那歡樂的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們心懷這樣的願景 積極地做著準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的日子非常充實而有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在非常期待節日的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 Redentore的日子到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們興奮期待的真正登場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…誰都不來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛到最後都沒跟我聯繫呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 郵遞員大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以上船了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我第一名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這次邀請的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子 我們來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部裝飾還算過關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個超級像雅典娜的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 上衣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 工作遲遲完成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就應該先跟我說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊 在那邊玩新婚夫婦對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 呀 真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家種的麝香葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼精神實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 差不多該把船划出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 我還以為妳不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳奶奶的身體怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給妳驚喜 所以沒跟妳聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我出差順便把她帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但比預定的時間稍晚了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您是小愛的姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她姐姐的丈夫 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次真是謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我現在馬上要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否請你們幫忙照顧愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 當然歡迎之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託幾位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快點開飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子開始餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 擺得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表很是不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 各位客人 今天歡迎來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…雖然僅僅是一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能夠共同度過這初秋之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無比地榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為這美好的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是什麼菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烤鴨和煮得軟軟的荷蘭豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個泡菜放了好多蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道非常奢華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝您的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤飯糰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢挑戰我的得意料理 膽子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在裡面夾了燒肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛肚子餓了吧 要多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個燒鴨可能不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}註：日文鴨子（かも）和可能（かも）同音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才那是用鴨子和可能來玩文字遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老頭子的冷笑話禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 餘興節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來由我和亞利亞社長一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓掌～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部裝飾很溫馨 讓大家都放鬆下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 妳們三人都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起待很長時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時大家的對話會暫時中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常自然而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜歡這樣的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來已經12點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把時間遺忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經意地關掉照明燈 很狡猾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 妳們也都過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是祖母的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼高興 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能夠得到邀請 真是謝謝妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托妳們三人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們度過了一個非常開心的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些人 如果沒有了妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就不會相識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美好邂逅的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好邂逅的…結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給我們製造了這美麗一瞬的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員的種子們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪花和風的聲音 我們終於相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到燈里姐姐 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們一起去尋找AQUA的美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去「希望之丘」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想坐坐水上電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}還有啊 還有啊…我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被浪花送來的溫馨一刻所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆星球 或許會永遠地守護著各種各樣的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雪白的溫馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
